---

<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center section-padding pt-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background orbs -->
  <div class="hero-orb-1 orb w-[600px] h-[600px] -top-40 -left-40"></div>
  <div class="hero-orb-2 orb w-[500px] h-[500px] -bottom-32 -right-32"></div>
  <div class="hero-orb-1 orb w-[300px] h-[300px] top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-10"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass-card mb-8">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Soluciones de IA disponibles ahora</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="reveal font-display font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl leading-[1.1] mb-8">
      <span class="text-white">Automatiza tu</span><br />
      <span class="text-white">negocio con </span>
      <span class="gradient-text">Inteligencia Artificial</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Diseñamos e implementamos soluciones de automatización y chatbots inteligentes
      que transforman la manera en que operas. <span class="text-white font-medium">Menos trabajo manual, más resultados.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn-primary text-lg">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
        </svg>
        Contactanos
      </a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="btn-outline text-lg">
        Ver Servicios
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Tech stack bar -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 mt-20 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 opacity-40">
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Tecnologías</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-8 text-slate-500">
        <span class="font-semibold">OpenAI</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span>
        <span class="font-semibold">n8n</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span>
        <span class="font-semibold">Python</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span>
        <span class="font-semibold">Node.js</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></span>
        <span class="font-semibold">WhatsApp API</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 animate-bounce">
    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Scroll</span>
    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
